### Ubiquiti Controller (internal Web API)
### Base URL is the Haus application server

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv HAUS_BASE_URL}}

### Get current snapshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ubiquiti
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Event callback - motion detected (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ubiquiti/event/motion?camera_id=ABC123&camera_name=Front+Door

### Event callback - smart detection (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ubiquiti/event/smart?type=person&camera_id=ABC123&camera_name=Front+Door&score=0.95

### Event callback - doorbell ring (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ubiquiti/event/ring?camera_id=ABC123&camera_name=Front+Door
